name.k: LEGO® 蝙蝠俠™3：飛越高譚市
LEGO®バットマン™3 ザ・ゲーム ゴッサムから宇宙へ

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The Dynamic Duo take to the stars in a brick-bashing adventure the whole family will love. As you travel from the Batcave to the Justice League Watchtower to deep space, hilarious banter and breezy puzzles make for classic LEGO®-game shenanigans. And with more than 100 playable characters—everyone from DC mainstays (The Flash, Wonder Woman, Sinestro) to delightful lesser-knowns (Etrigan, Plastic Man, Stargirl)—the fan service is unreal.
